<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi there, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      Someone requested a password reset for your account on polsci630. Click the following link to reset the password.
